snippet.title: Cooking Simulator VR - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1358140/Cooking_Simulator_VR/
Discord: https://discord.gg/YuKhZ27

Find us also here:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gameboomvr/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GBoomVR
TikTok: http://vm.tiktok.com/Jev21aS

Become the ultimate chef in VR! Take control of a highly polished, realistic kitchen equipped with all kinds of utensils and stands. Unlock and master over 80 recipes or use dozens of lifelike ingredients to cook everything you like. A simulator spiced up with a dash of real-life physics!
